                        .w3-container.w3-card-2.w3-white
                            h2.w3-text-grey.w3-padding-16
                                i.fa.fa-building.fa-fw.w3-margin-right.w3-xxlarge.w3-text-blue
                                | Work Experience
                            .w3-container
                                h5.w3-opacity
                                    b Shanghai Data Solutions Co.
                                h6.w3-text-blue
                                    i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                                    | June 2015 - August 2017
                                li Network Engineer
                                li Set up network service links, configured server ports.
                                li Provided network services thorough clients requests in Internet Data Center (IDC).
                                li Large-scale server trouble shooting and maintenance.
                                hr
                            .w3-container
                                h5.w3-opacity
                                    b Balance Electronics
                                h6.w3-text-blue
                                    i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                                    | June 2014 - August 2017
                                li Network Engineer
                                li Local area network (LANs) analysis and maintenance.
                                li Network designing and implementation.

                                hr
                        .w3-container.w3-card-2.w3-white
                            h2.w3-text-grey.w3-padding-16
                                i.fa.fa-sitemap.fa-fw.w3-margin-right.w3-xxlarge.w3-text-blue
                                | Projects
                            .w3-container
                                h5.w3-opacity
                                    b Android controlled robot cart
                                li Designed and built a battery driven 4-motor robot car with robotic arm, video camera, and Field Programming Gates Array (FPGA) chip board.
                                li Created an android application as the controller to send the control signal via Wi-Fi module to the FPGA board, and receive the video information from the video camera.
                                li The robot car can move around, pick up objectives, and send back video signals as the android application control it.
                                li The project was designed to have applications in rescuing effort and scientific surveys.
                                hr
                            .w3-container
                                h5.w3-opacity
                                    b Real time peer-to-peer (P2P) file sharing system
                                li Developed an indexing server containing a list of files registered in the system, and multiple peer clients who own the files.
                                li The peer communicates with the indexing server to locate required file and download from other peers, with real time update in file system.
                                li Java Eclipse with Remote Methods Invocation (RMI) were used in the development.
                                li This program was designed to satisfy uses cases for small businesses.
                                hr
                            .w3-container
                                h5.w3-opacity
                                    b Image enhancement system for image reconstruction and image recovery
                                li Applied Prewitt operators to reduce noises and realize edge enhancement.
                                li Implemented pseudoinverse filter to remove image motion blur.
                                li Implemented tomography algorithm to realize digital image reconstruction.
